DROP ROLE ADMIN_HDSK;

CREATE ROLE ADMIN_HDSK NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Object privileges granted to ADMIN_HDSK
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.DET_TICKET TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT EXECUTE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.FUN_BLOQUEOS TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT EXECUTE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.FUN_GET_IP_MACHINE TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT EXECUTE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.FUN_GET_PERFIL TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT EXECUTE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.FUN_ROL_ASIGNADO TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.HOJAS_DE_SOPORTE TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.IMAGES TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.NOVEDAD TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT SELECT ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.NUM_DETALLE_TICKET_SEQ TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT EXECUTE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.PRO_KILL_SESSIONS TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT EXECUTE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.PRO_LOAD_FILE TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.TICKET TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.TIPO_ERROR TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.TIPO_NOVEDAD TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.TIPO_NOVEDADES TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.TIPO_USUARIOS TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.USUARIOS TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT SELECT ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.VW_CAB_TIKETS TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT SELECT ON GEOVANNY_DELGADO.VW_DET_TIKETS TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT SELECT ON NOMINA.CATEGORIA_CARGO TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT SELECT ON NOMINA.PERSONAL TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT SELECT ON NOMINA.PERSONAL_CARGO TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT SELECT ON NOMINA.TIPO_EMPLEADO TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT EXECUTE ON OPEBDD.PRO_MATAR_SESIONES TO ADMIN_HDSK;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.DBA_ROLES TO ADMIN_HDSK;

-- System privileges granted to ADMIN_HDSK
GRANT SELECT ANY DICTIONARY TO ADMIN_HDSK;

DROP ROLE AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;

CREATE ROLE AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Object privileges granted to AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.AQ$INTERNET_USERS TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.AQ$_PROPAGATION_STATUS TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.DBA_AQ_AGENT_PRIVS TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.DBA_AQ_AGENTS TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.DBA_QUEUES TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.DBA_QUEUE_SCHEDULES TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.DBA_QUEUE_SUBSCRIBERS TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.DBA_QUEUE_TABLES TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQ TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQADM TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQELM TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQ_IMPORT_INTERNAL TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQIN TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQJMS_INTERNAL TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_RULE_EXIMP TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_TRANSFORM TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.GV_$AQ TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.V_$AQ TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.AQ$WM$EVENT_QUEUE_TABLE TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.AQ$WM$EVENT_QUEUE_TABLE_R TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.AQ$WM$EVENT_QUEUE_TABLE_S TO AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE;

-- System privileges granted to AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE
BEGIN
SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.GRANT_SYSTEM_PRIVILEGE(
  PRIVILEGE    => SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.CREATE_EVALUATION_CONTEXT_OBJ,
  GRANTEE      => 'AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE',
  GRANT_OPTION => TRUE);
END;
/
BEGIN
SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.GRANT_SYSTEM_PRIVILEGE(
  PRIVILEGE    => SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.CREATE_RULE_OBJ,
  GRANTEE      => 'AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE',
  GRANT_OPTION => TRUE);
END;
/
BEGIN
SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.GRANT_SYSTEM_PRIVILEGE(
  PRIVILEGE    => SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.CREATE_RULE_SET_OBJ,
  GRANTEE      => 'AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE',
  GRANT_OPTION => TRUE);
END;
/
BEGIN
SYS.DBMS_AQADM.GRANT_SYSTEM_PRIVILEGE (
  PRIVILEGE    => 'DEQUEUE_ANY',
  GRANTEE      => 'AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE',
  ADMIN_OPTION => TRUE);
END;
/
BEGIN
SYS.DBMS_AQADM.GRANT_SYSTEM_PRIVILEGE (
  PRIVILEGE    => 'ENQUEUE_ANY',
  GRANTEE      => 'AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE',
  ADMIN_OPTION => TRUE);
END;
/
BEGIN
SYS.DBMS_AQADM.GRANT_SYSTEM_PRIVILEGE (
  PRIVILEGE    => 'MANAGE_ANY',
  GRANTEE      => 'AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE',
  ADMIN_OPTION => TRUE);
END;
/

-- Grantees of AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE
GRANT AQ_ADMINISTRATOR_ROLE TO SYS WITH ADMIN OPTION;



DROP ROLE AQ_USER_ROLE;

CREATE ROLE AQ_USER_ROLE NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Object privileges granted to AQ_USER_ROLE
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQ TO AQ_USER_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQIN TO AQ_USER_ROLE;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQJMS_INTERNAL TO AQ_USER_ROLE;

  (GRANTEE_NAME   => 'DBA', 
   PRIVILEGE_NAME => 'ADMINISTER_RESOURCE_MANAGER',
   ADMIN_OPTION   => TRUE);
END;
/

GRANT ALTER ANY DIMENSION TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;

  GRANT_OPTION => TRUE);

GRANT DROP ANY CONTEXT TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT DROP ANY DIMENSION TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT DROP ANY DIRECTORY TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
BEGIN
SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.GRANT_SYSTEM_PRIVILEGE(
  PRIVILEGE    => SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.DROP_ANY_EVALUATION_CONTEXT,
  GRANTEE      => 'DBA',
  GRANT_OPTION => TRUE);
END;
/
GRANT DROP ANY INDEX TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT DROP ANY INDEXTYPE TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT DROP ANY LIBRARY TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT DROP ANY MATERIALIZED VIEW TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT DROP ANY OPERATOR TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT DROP ANY OUTLINE TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT DROP ANY PROCEDURE TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT DROP ANY ROLE TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
BEGIN

  PRIVILEGE    => SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.DROP_ANY_RULE,
  GRANTEE      => 'DBA',
  GRANT_OPTION => TRUE);
END;
/
BEGIN

  PRIVILEGE    => SYS.DBMS_RULE_ADM.DROP_ANY_RULE_SET,
  GRANTEE      => 'DBA',
  GRANT_OPTION => TRUE);
END;

   PRIVILEGE_NAME => 'ADMINISTER_RESOURCE_MANAGER',
   ADMIN_OPTION   => FALSE);
END;

DROP ROLE LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;

CREATE ROLE LABORATORISTA_CLINICO NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Object privileges granted to LABORATORISTA_CLINICO
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.COMPLEMENTOS_A_RESULTADOS TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.COMPORTAMIENTOS_GERMEN TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.DETALLES_DE_EXAMENES TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.DIAGNOSTICOS TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.EXAMENES TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.EXM_TRANSMITIDOS TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.GERMENES_DE_PRUEBAS TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SIS.LBREST TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SIS.LBRPCKLBR TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.PAPANICOLAOUS TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.PLANTILLAS TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.RANGOS_DE_NORMALIDAD TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.RANGOS_NORMALIDAD_COMPLEMENTOS TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.SLCROCHE_SEQ TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.SOLICITUDES_ROCHE_CABECERA TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT ON SIS.SOLICITUDES_ROCHE_CABECERA_JN TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.SOLICITUDES_ROCHE_DETALLE TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT ON SIS.SOLICITUDES_ROCHE_DETALLE_JN TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.TURNOS_DE_CLINICO TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.TURNOS_DE_EXAMENES TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.TURNOS_DE_LABORATORIOS TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT ON SIS.TURNOS_DE_LABORATORIOS_JN TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.VARIABLES_DE_EXAMENES TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;

GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.VARIABLES_PLANTILLAS TO LABORATORISTA_CLINICO;

DROP ROLE MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;

CREATE ROLE MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Object privileges granted to MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE
GRANT EXECUTE ON SIS.BSANGRE TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.DETALLES_TRANSFUSIONES TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.DETALLES_TRANSFUSION_FINALES TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.DONACIONES TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.DONANTES TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.FRACCIONAMIENTOS TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.FRACCIONES TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.LINEAS_ENTREVISTAS TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.PREGUNTAS_ENTREVISTAS TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.PRUEBAS_SANGUINEAS TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.PRUEBAS_SEROLOGICAS TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.SOLICITUDES_TRANSFUSIONES TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.TRANSFUSIONES TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.UNIDADES TO MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE;

-- Roles granted to MEDICOS_BANCOSANGRE

DROP ROLE MICROBIOLOGIA;

CREATE ROLE MICROBIOLOGIA NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Object privileges granted to MICROBIOLOGIA
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.ANTIBIOTICOS TO MICROBIOLOGIA;

GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.COMPORTAMIENTOS_GERMEN TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.DETALLES_DE_EXAMENES TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.EXAMENES TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.GERMENES TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE ON SIS.GERMENES_DE_PRUEBAS TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.RANGOS_DE_NORMALIDAD TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.RANGOS_NORMALIDAD_COMPLEMENTOS TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.SOLICITUDES_DE_EXAMENES TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.TIPOS_DE_DATOS TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.VARIABLES_DE_EXAMENES TO MICROBIOLOGIA;
GRANT SELECT ON SIS.VARIABLES_DE_EXAMENES_03082012 TO MICROBIOLOGIA;

DROP ROLE OEM_MONITOR;

CREATE ROLE OEM_MONITOR NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Object privileges granted to OEM_MONITOR
GRANT SELECT ON DBSNMP.MGMT_BASELINE TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT SELECT ON DBSNMP.MGMT_BASELINE_SQL TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT SELECT ON DBSNMP.MGMT_HISTORY TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT SELECT ON DBSNMP.MGMT_HISTORY_SQL TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT SELECT ON DBSNMP.MGMT_LATEST TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT SELECT ON DBSNMP.MGMT_LATEST_SQL TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT EXECUTE ON DBSNMP.MGMT_RESPONSE TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT EXECUTE ON DBSNMP.MGMT_UPDATE_DB_FEATURE_LOG TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQ TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_AQADM TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_DRS TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_MONITOR TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_SERVER_ALERT TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_SYSTEM TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT EXECUTE ON SYS.DBMS_WORKLOAD_REPOSITORY TO OEM_MONITOR;

-- System privileges granted to OEM_MONITOR
GRANT ADVISOR TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT ANALYZE ANY TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT ANALYZE ANY DICTIONARY TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT CREATE JOB TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT CREATE SESSION TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT CREATE TABLE TO OEM_MONITOR;
BEGIN
SYS.DBMS_AQADM.GRANT_SYSTEM_PRIVILEGE (
  PRIVILEGE    => 'MANAGE_ANY',
  GRANTEE      => 'OEM_MONITOR',
  ADMIN_OPTION => FALSE);
END;
/
GRANT SELECT ANY DICTIONARY TO OEM_MONITOR;

-- Roles granted to OEM_MONITOR
GRANT CONNECT TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT RESOURCE TO OEM_MONITOR;
GRANT SELECT_CATALOG_ROLE TO OEM_MONITOR;

-- Grantees of OEM_MONITOR
GRANT OEM_MONITOR TO DBSNMP;
GRANT OEM_MONITOR TO SYS WITH ADMIN OPTION;

DROP ROLE SALES_HISTORY_ROLE;

CREATE ROLE SALES_HISTORY_ROLE NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- System privileges granted to SALES_HISTORY_ROLE
GRANT CREATE ANY DIRECTORY TO SALES_HISTORY_ROLE;
GRANT CREATE DIMENSION TO SALES_HISTORY_ROLE;
GRANT CREATE MATERIALIZED VIEW TO SALES_HISTORY_ROLE;
GRANT DROP ANY DIRECTORY TO SALES_HISTORY_ROLE;
GRANT QUERY REWRITE TO SALES_HISTORY_ROLE;

-- Grantees of SALES_HISTORY_ROLE
GRANT SALES_HISTORY_ROLE TO SYSTEM WITH ADMIN OPTION;



DROP ROLE SCHEDULER_ADMIN;

CREATE ROLE SCHEDULER_ADMIN NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- System privileges granted to SCHEDULER_ADMIN

GRANT CREATE EXTERNAL JOB TO SCHEDULER_ADMIN WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT CREATE JOB TO SCHEDULER_ADMIN WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT EXECUTE ANY CLASS TO SCHEDULER_ADMIN WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT EXECUTE ANY PROGRAM TO SCHEDULER_ADMIN WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT MANAGE SCHEDULER TO SCHEDULER_ADMIN WITH ADMIN OPTION;

-- Grantees of SCHEDULER_ADMIN
GRANT SCHEDULER_ADMIN TO DBA WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT SCHEDULER_ADMIN TO SYS WITH ADMIN OPTION;

DROP ROLE WKUSER;

CREATE ROLE WKUSER NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- System privileges granted to WKUSER
GRANT CREATE CLUSTER TO WKUSER;
GRANT CREATE PROCEDURE TO WKUSER;
GRANT CREATE TABLE TO WKUSER;
GRANT CREATE TRIGGER TO WKUSER;
GRANT CREATE TYPE TO WKUSER;

-- Roles granted to WKUSER
GRANT CONNECT TO WKUSER;

-- Grantees of WKUSER
GRANT WKUSER TO SYS WITH ADMIN OPTION;



DROP ROLE WM_ADMIN_ROLE;

CREATE ROLE WM_ADMIN_ROLE NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Object privileges granted to WM_ADMIN_ROLE
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.AQ$WM$EVENT_QUEUE_TABLE TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.AQ$WM$EVENT_QUEUE_TABLE_R TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.AQ$WM$EVENT_QUEUE_TABLE_S TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.DBA_REMOVED_WORKSPACES TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.DBA_WM_SYS_PRIVS TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.DBA_WM_VERSIONED_TABLES TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.DBA_WM_VT_ERRORS TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.DBA_WORKSPACE_PRIVS TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.DBA_WORKSPACES TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.DBA_WORKSPACE_SAVEPOINTS TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.DBA_WORKSPACE_SESSIONS TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.WM_COMPRESS_BATCH_SIZES TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;
GRANT SELECT ON WMSYS.WM_COMPRESSIBLE_TABLES TO WM_ADMIN_ROLE;

-- Grantees of WM_ADMIN_ROLE
GRANT WM_ADMIN_ROLE TO DBA;
GRANT WM_ADMIN_ROLE TO SYSTEM;
GRANT WM_ADMIN_ROLE TO WMSYS WITH ADMIN OPTION;



DROP ROLE XDBADMIN;

CREATE ROLE XDBADMIN NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Object privileges granted to XDBADMIN
GRANT SELECT ON SYS.DBA_EPG_DAD_AUTHORIZATION TO XDBADMIN;
GRANT ALTER, DELETE, INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE, ON COMMIT REFRESH, QUERY REWRITE, DEBUG, FLASHBACK ON XDB.XDB$CONFIG TO XDBADMIN;

-- Roles granted to XDBADMIN
GRANT XDBWEBSERVICES TO XDBADMIN;

-- Grantees of XDBADMIN
GRANT XDBADMIN TO DBA;
GRANT XDBADMIN TO SYS WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT XDBADMIN TO SYSTEM;



DROP ROLE XDBWEBSERVICES;

CREATE ROLE XDBWEBSERVICES NOT IDENTIFIED;

-- Grantees of XDBWEBSERVICES
GRANT XDBWEBSERVICES TO DBA;
GRANT XDBWEBSERVICES TO SYS WITH ADMIN OPTION;
GRANT XDBWEBSERVICES TO XDBADMIN;
